section "Poisson and Gaussian noise"
option "poisson" - "Comma-separated pre-log Poisson noise parameters: I0 pre-log normalization and (optional) pre-exp multiplicative factor (default 0.01879 mm^-1, attenuation coefficient of water at 75 keV)" double multiple no
option "gaussian" - "Additive Gaussian noise standard deviation (pre-log if --poisson given, without exp/log otherwise)" double no
